> even though it was running only on 2 cylinders.  Then I put #3 and #4 
> back and pulled #1 and #2 and it ran kinda crappy on that side (not as 
> well as running on #1 and #2 and there were a few thumps here and 
> there.
>
> So, I'm thinking maybe an exhaust leak on the driver's side?  Any 
> thoughts on what to do next?

